    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s in flawless shape! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one\u2014always garaged, never a scratch, and the interior still has that fresh new-car scent. It\u2019s a dream to drive and looks stunning from every angle. If you want the best of the best without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
