    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering, featuring the legendary S54B32 inline-six with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This specimen is mechanically flawless, boasting a documented rod bearing service and a fully reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural integrity. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission delivers crisp, tactile shifts, paired with a factory-spec variable M differential lock for optimal power delivery. With a pristine undercarriage and zero bushing deflection, this concours-level example offers a pure, analog driving experience that is increasingly rare.",
      "price": 48500.0,
