      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since its original purchase. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, scratches, or stone chips. Inside, the cabin remains in a pristine state; the premium leather upholstery still retains its factory scent, and every electronic component functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a fully documented service history from authorized dealerships. It has never seen inclement weather, and the undercarriage is as clean as the body. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the factory. Includes all original manuals, two sets of keys, and a custom-fitted car cover.",
