      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she\u2019s a total stunner. This car is in truly pristine condition\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it tucked away in the garage, and the interior is still flawless. It drives like an absolute dream and needs zero work. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically perfect, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out if you want to take a look!",
