      "description": "Offered is an impeccable example of the E92 M3, featuring the legendary S65 4.0L V8 with individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline. This specimen retains its factory-original paint depth and shows zero signs of subframe fatigue or rod bearing wear. Power is delivered via the M Double-Clutch Transmission (DCT) to an M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring optimal torque vectoring. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC), providing a surgically precise interface between the pilot and the tarmac. Meticulously maintained with a documented service history, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated Bavarian engineering.",
